{"tid":527440,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"見到咁多打手吹奏誇世代係超越天與地嘅反共神劇，我頭先就開電視機睇下，睇完真係得啖笑","createTime":"2018-01-12T15:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T11:52:41.000Z","uid":55552,"like":22,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdc6a2b3eef23ceffdcbefa261c08c8f569a2c9","tid":527440,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"原來只要香港人阻止到大財團係香港起核電站，唔好搞到核爆，我哋香港係中共嘅英明統治底下去到2047就會人人有樓住，經濟繁榮到買嘢都唔洗就住就住㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前兩日班傻仔仲攞住&quot;唔通妄想2047仲係假&quot;張圖嚟劣到成地精，又話TVB反了、編劇係連登仔又剩，結果原來此2047非彼2047，編劇借住反核奶共奶到雪雪聲，真係一巴巴車落班打手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成班打飛機射錯人，真係慘慘豬</span></span>"},{"pid":"56b466658e9a94346740385b19bd89d7881c9574","tid":527440,"uid":55552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"TVB打手駁唔到，只能默默留下負皮，死狗般夾著尾巴離去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8809a43bfbfd33575c8e9f67c4ac17b89fba3183","tid":527440,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cbd87b5e80f11d890f1019eac1be421ee9b69b","tid":527440,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24077d1589b4ee42ef194e553ccf60e11b0bc596","tid":527440,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90cbd87b5e80f11d890f1019eac1be421ee9b69b","tid":527440,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦你"},{"pid":"9a69d4edce47a6fc29658c1b34102c6865014fd0","tid":527